Added DatabaseInterface, and more semantic changes to Duplexer.
Added a simple test client for the server. Server functionality should fully work now.
Added final to the queues to synchronize on.

Added the beginnings of the java server implementation: Server.java, CommunicationProtocol.java, Duplexer.java
